<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ الأَعْرابيِّ:</span> هُوَ <span class="c2">(الفَسادُ)</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(قالَ: ( {والتَّوَخُّنُ: القَصْدُ إِلَى خَيرٍ أَو شَرَ)</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
